<div>
	<div class="banner banner-involved">
		<div class="container_12">
		 	<div class="banner-box push_1 grid_10">
		 		<h1 class="grid_12">We depend on your generous contributions.</h1>
		 		<div class="rule push_4 grid_4"></div>
		 		<p class="banner-txt grid_12">We appreciate your involvement with PMVC.</p>
		 	</div>
		 </div>
	</div>
	<div class="star-wrapper">	
		<%= image_tag("star-blue.svg", :alt => "star", class:"blue-star") %>
	</div>
		
	<div class="intro">
		<div class="container_12">
			<p class="intro-txt alpha push_2 grid_8 omega">We encourage giving to PMVC in three ways: a gift of your <em>time</em>, a gift of <em>money</em>, or a gift of a <em>wish list item</em>.</p>
		<div class="black-rule alpha push_1 grid_10 omega"></div>
		</div>
	</div>
	
		<div class="container_12">
			<h2 class="alpha prefix_1 grid_11"><span class="blue-bar">VOLUNTEER WITH US</span></h2>
				<div class="alpha prefix_1 grid_6">
					<p class="section-txt">We are always looking for more help connecting local veterans! If you would like to get involved with us, here's what we need:</p>
				</div>
				
				
				<div class="grid_5">
					<form id="form1" name="form1" class="wufoo topLabel page" accept-charset="UTF-8" autocomplete="off" enctype="multipart/form-data" method="post" novalidate
				    action="https://pmvc.wufoo.com/forms/zk9mz940bjepjn/#public">
					  				
					<ul>
					<li id="foli12" class="notranslate section-txt-blue form-box  float">
					<div>
						<input Placeholder="Name" id="Field12" name="Field12" type="text" class="field text medium" value="" maxlength="255" tabindex="1" onkeyup="" required />
					</div>
					</li><li id="foli13" class="notranslate section-txt-blue form-box float">
					<div>
						<input Placeholder="Email" id="Field13" name="Field13" type="text" class="field text medium" value="" maxlength="255" tabindex="2" onkeyup="" required />
					</div>
						</li><li id="foli14" class="notranslate section-txt-blue form-box float">
					<div>
						<input Placeholder="Address" id="Field14" name="Field14" type="text" class="field text medium" value="" maxlength="255" tabindex="3" onkeyup="" required />
					</div>
						</li><li id="foli15" class="notranslate section-txt-blue form-box float">
						<label class="desc " id="title15" for="Field15">
					<div>
						<input Placeholder="Phone" id="Field15" name="Field15" type="text" class="field text nospin medium"  value="" tabindex="4" onkeyup="" required />
					</div>
					</li>
					<li class="buttons ">
					<div>
						<input id="saveForm" name="saveForm" class="btTxt submit submit-button form-box grid_6 omega float" type="submit" value="Submit"/></div>
					</li>
					<li class="hide">
						<input type="hidden" id="idstamp" name="idstamp" value="CDqV62kDzQ1OVp/+3tS9H2v1l2SREcM4jtaaoHE7vvo=" />
					</li>
					</ul>
					</form> 	
				</div>
		
			<h2 class="alpha prefix_1 grid_11"><span class="blue-bar">DONATE MONEY</span></h2>
				<div class="alpha prefix_1 grid_6"> 
				<p class="section-txt">Want to help us do what we do? We rely on contributions from the community to connect and help our veterans and their friends and family! We would love your generous support!</p>
				</div>
				<div class="grid_5 omega">
					<p class="section-txt">You may also send a check to:<br>
					4837 NE Couch St<br>Portland, OR 97213<br>
					Call to make a gift by phone<br>
					(503)238-6428<br><br>
					<a href="" class="submit-button alpha grid_7">PMVC PAYPAL</a>
				</div>
				
			<h2 class="alpha prefix_1 grid_11"><span class="blue-bar">OUR WISHLIST</span></h2>
			<div class="section-txt alpha prefix_1 grid_6 suffix_5">
				<p class="section-txt">We have a list of specific items we would love to have for our events!</p>
			</div>
			<div class="section-txt alpha prefix_1 grid_6 suffix_5 omega">
				<em>Sports equipment (basketballs, footballs, frisbees, fishing gear) board games, books, painting supplies.</em>
			</div>
			<div class="black-rule alpha push_1 grid_5"></div>
			<div class="section-txt page-margin alpha prefix_1 grid_5 suffix_6 omega">
				<p class="section-txt">Have an item you would like to give? Contact us directly at <a href="mailto:info@pmvc.com">info@pmvc.com.</a></p>
			</div>
		</div>

</div>